694
00:40:58,290 --> 00:41:00,375
ARCHER: WHERE'S T'POL?

695
00:41:00,417 --> 00:41:04,003
TUCKER: UH, SHE'S IN DECON
WITH DR. PHLOX.

696
00:41:04,045 --> 00:41:06,505
ARCHER: WHAT HAPPENED?

697
00:41:06,547 --> 00:41:08,800
REED: IT'S A LONG STORY.

698
00:41:08,841 --> 00:41:09,968
[BEEPS]

699
00:41:10,009 --> 00:41:11,719
HOSHI:
YOU'RE BEING HAILED, CAPTAIN.

700
00:41:13,805 --> 00:41:16,057
SKALAAR:
<i>I SEE YOU MADE IT BACK SAFELY.</i>

701
00:41:16,099 --> 00:41:17,642
ARCHER: DO YOU THINK
THE KLINGONS KNOW

