707
00:41:30,071 --> 00:41:31,906
ARCHER: I'LL KEEP MY EYES OPEN.

708
00:41:31,948 --> 00:41:34,492
SKALAAR:
<i>BE CAREFUL, CAPTAIN.</i>

709
00:41:34,533 --> 00:41:37,912
<i>IT'S LIKELY THE KLINGONS</i>
